## ğŸš€ **Quick Start**

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.11+
- Telegram Bot Token (from [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather))
- Admin Telegram User ID

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/abraxas0001/Bhaichara-Bot.git
